ORIGINAL DESCRIPTION
Asson...

The adventure never stops! From 1999 to the end of 2007! 
Shadowmans soul does never die!

fy_asson is a tribute of the game "Shadowman" from 1999
I just had the idea to do a little smart map nearly to the good old times!

It's a Fight yard - rush - horror - sniper map! 
Have fun with this map! The famous mapper X-tr3m3r & Syco* finally made it.

************************************

AUTHOR'S DESCRIPTION

This is a map made upon request for the ex-member Syco*. It is a heavily modified version of gg_woods which can be found here:

http://gamebanana.com/cssgg/maps/40961

The map features an open field area with natural cover provided by sand hills and an underground long corridor. This is a really straight forward map, good for gg too.
